title: Formula 1 2013 Round 19 Brazil Qualifying.SkyF1
description:
Coverage of the qualifying session of the 2013 brazilian grand prix.
It is up delayed cause of the weather conditions at the racetrac.
Video starts 5 minutes before the session and ends with the cars entering parc ferme.
Sorry for that. This is my first weekend, i ever recorded and uploaded on tpb.
Guess the quality is good now. 
Leave me a comment if you want.
Hope you enjoy.
